Class SimpleShell

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.unb.cic.bionimbus.client.shell.SimpleShell

  • public final class SimpleShell
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple shell to interface with BioNimbus. Lacking features: No up arrow down arrow (circular buffer) No pipe | or redirection > No autocomplete
